name: Rosita_Woven_Jacquard_20-inch_Toss_Pillow_(Set_of_2)
reviews: This pillow is soft yet firm. You may notice in the photo that the lines of color appear more faintly at the top of the pillow. This faintness actually appears in the pillow. The brown background does not have the same intensity throughout. It is a pretty pillow, though.
I like the design on the pillows and the are firm I would recommend these

These pillows are beautiful. It's been a long time since I've seen such quality. They look a lot more expensive than expected. Best part is my hubby never likes anything but he loved these. I would recommend to anyone who wants to try
Handsome, full pillows that look great on my beige sofa. The colors are true to the photograph.
Cheap looking! Could not return because of an $11 return shipping fee.
Really nice full pillows. Colors even nicer than pictured. Am very pleased.
The pillows are even nicer than the photos!
Just got them in. Looks perfect with new bedspread.
These pillows are much prettier in person, big and fluffy, well made, love them!
description:
The Rosita woven Jacquard toss pillows features mod florals with
"pops" of medallions coming together beautifully in this carefully
woven toss pillows. The fabric is soft and subtle and can work as a
stand alone pillow or mixed with other styles. The pillows are
filled with premium fiber preventing the corners from flopping over
and the body from having dead spots.
